com.progstock.controller

Class PrincipalUi

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.progstock.controller.PrincipalUi
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class PrincipalUi
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    PrincipalUi is the class that represents the main window of the program.

    PrincipalUi contains the different pages of the program, as well as their respective controller.
